OL,3,CLondon temperatures to jump 10C by
OL,4,CFriday for hottest day of year so far
OL,6,FTemperatures could hit 28C in London
OL,7,Fon Friday in what is expected to be
OL,8,Fthe hottest day of the year so far,
OL,9,Ffollowing an unusually cool May.
OL,11,FIt has been colder than average for
OL,12,Fmost after temperatures dropped in the
OL,13,Ffirst week of the month, the Met
OL,14,FOffice said.
OL,16,FThe warm weather returning to England
OL,17,Fand Wales on Friday is predicted to
OL,18,Flinger into next week.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
