OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779879767
OL,3,CLondon temperatures to jump 10C by
OL,4,CFriday for hottest day of year so far
OL,6,FClouds and thundery showers could
OL,7,Fhinder Saturday's heat but if they do
OL,8,Fnot appear then temperatures could
OL,9,Fexceed Friday's.
OL,11,FA heatwave in the capital would then
OL,12,Fbe possible by Sunday, Met Office
OL,13,Foperational meteorologist Niamh Murray
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FThe heatwave threshold for London at
OL,17,Fthis time of year is 28C for three
OL,18,Fconsecutive days in the same location.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
