CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779879767
OL,3,CLondon temperatures to jump 10C by
OL,4,CFriday for hottest day of year so far
OL,6,FNiamh Murray said: "If temperatures
OL,7,Fhold up on Saturday, we are expected
OL,8,Fto keep high pressure around into at
OL,9,Fleast the first half of next week, so
OL,10,Fthere is a potential that we may see
OL,11,Fthose thresholds reached by the time
OL,12,Fwe get to Sunday but... it's not 100%
OL,13,Fcertain on that yet."
