OL,3,CLondon temperatures to jump 10C by
OL,4,CFriday for hottest day of year so far
OL,6,FThe contrast with the recent cool
OL,7,Fspell will make the weekend feel much
OL,8,Fwarmer, she added.
OL,10,FMost of England and Wales, as well as
OL,11,Fparts of Scotland, will see above
OL,12,Faverage temperatures.
OL,14,FThe east coast could see mid to high
OL,15,F20Cs, while Wales and western parts of
OL,16,Fthe north of England may reach 25C.
OL,18,FThe hottest weather will be in the
OL,19,Fsouth-east, particularly around
OL,20,FLondon, and potentially towards East
OL,21,FAnglia.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
