PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779879767
OL,3,CLondon temperatures to jump 10C by
OL,4,CFriday for hottest day of year so far
OL,6,FUK-wide highs for this time of year
OL,7,Fare 15.5C and recent temperatures have
OL,8,Fpeaked at about 14C.
OL,10,FThe hottest day of the year so far was
OL,11,F26.6C in Kew Gardens, west London, on
OL,12,FApril 8.
OL,14,FFurther showers are forecast on
OL,15,FWednesday though they will be lighter
OL,16,Fand more isolated, Ms Murray said.
OL,18,FThursday will start cloudy for
OL,19,Feverybody with some rain in Wales and
OL,20,Fparts of north-west England
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
