OL,3,CLondon temperatures to jump 10C by
OL,4,CFriday for hottest day of year so far
OL,6,FThe weather will brighten for many by
OL,7,Fthe afternoon as the clouds break up,
OL,8,Fparticularly in the south.
OL,10,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,11,Four political experts are across all
OL,12,Fthe latest key talking points.
